quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,1,"O you enveloped in your cloak!",footnotes:182393:1
  74,2,"Arise, and warn,",footnotes:182394:1
  74,3,"and magnify the glory of your Lord,",footnotes:182395:1
  74,4,"and purify your robes,",footnotes:182396:1
  74,5,"and shun uncleanness,",footnotes:182397:1
  74,6,"and bestow not favour in order to seek from others a greater return,",footnotes:182398:1
  74,7,"and persevere for your Lord's sake.",footnotes:182399:1
  74,8,"When the Trumpet shall be sounded,"
  74,9,"that will surely be a hard day,",footnotes:182400:1
  74,10,"not an easy day for the unbelievers.",footnotes:182401:1